data.description: This Charming 3 Bedroom 2.5 bath home was built in 2013. Once entering through the main door way you will be greeted by a spacious open floor plan with a living room that blends into a comfortable dining room. The kitchen is conveniently placed towards the east side of the home, with a large island area and beautiful granite countertops you will definitely find an excellent an entertaining area for your friends and family. All three bedrooms are comfortably sized with great natural lighting and there is even an additional room that serves as an office located on the west side of the homes lower level. The back yard is a great size for a small family and is low maintenance, if you find that the grass area is not enough for the kiddos, no worries there is a community park that only takes one minute to walk to. Washer, Dryer and Refrigerator included with the sale of the home, schedule your appointment today!
